OL,4,Cinvestigation: What are the rules?
OL,6,FThe developments and use of the term
OL,7,F"inside information" has prompted much
OL,8,Fonline debate around what exactly
OL,9,Fcould merit a breach of the rules. But
OL,10,Fwhat are they? ITV News explains.
OL,12,FWhat is inside information?
OL,14,FInside information is best known in
OL,15,Fthe context of the financial world,
OL,16,Fwhere trading with such knowledge is
OL,17,Flisted as a criminal offence in every
OL,18,Fmajor economy.
