OL,6,FCheating is categorised as consisting
OL,7,Fof "actual or attempted deception or
OL,8,Finterference".
OL,10,FAnyone found guilty of this offence
OL,11,Fcan face up to two years in prison and
OL,12,Fa fine, and the commission has the
OL,13,Fpower to prosecute those accused of
OL,14,Fbreaching the rules.
