OL,3,CTory candidates face election betting
OL,4,Cinvestigation: What are the rules?
OL,6,FThe Gambling Commission largely relies
OL,7,Fon its sports betting integrity unit
OL,8,F(SBIU) to monitor any cheating
OL,9,Fbreaches. Again, this is because the
OL,10,Fmajority of bets placed relate to
OL,11,Fsport.
OL,13,FThe SBIU deals with reports of
OL,14,F"betting-related corruption" and works
OL,15,Fclosely with a separate team to
OL,16,Fenforce the same processes to non-
OL,17,Fsporting events.
