OL,6,FIn a statement, the Gambling
OL,7,FCommission said: "Currently the
OL,8,Fcommission is investigating the
OL,9,Fpossibility of offences concerning the
OL,10,Fdate of the election.
OL,12,F"This is an ongoing investigation, and
OL,13,Fthe commission cannot provide any
OL,14,Ffurther details at this time."
OL,16,FRishi Sunak said Tory figures who are
OL,17,Ffound to have broken gambling rules
OL,18,F"should face the full force of the
OL,19,Flaw".
